# Script Standards

## Header

Every script needs a shebang + comment block: one-line description, longer description, usage, prerequisites.


## Structure

Scripts over ~50 lines: break into `step_N_*()` functions with a `main()` entry point called at bottom (see `install.sh`).

Never mention `just`, `justfile`

## Comments

Every function needs a purpose comment.
